    "description": "<br><br>Fluffy Smash is a free-for-all cat fighting high-paced game. Pick your cat wisely and start the war. RAWR! <br>Destruct your opponents! Meow! <br>TAKE OVER THE WORLD! MEOW! 😼<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142960/extras/ee698724db780c1631c6ec33ef46af40.poster.avif?t=1667732391\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142960/extras/ee698724db780c1631c6ec33ef46af40.webm?t=1667732391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142960/extras/ee698724db780c1631c6ec33ef46af40.mp4?t=1667732391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong> 🐈 CATS 🐈</strong><br>An ever growing roster of cats to pick from. We are continuously adding new cats with different unique playstyles. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142960/extras/0cf68acc0032b69c492c9de8eba1c030.poster.avif?t=1667732391\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142960/extras/0cf68acc0032b69c492c9de8eba1c030.webm?t=1667732391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142960/extras/0cf68acc0032b69c492c9de8eba1c030.mp4?t=1667732391\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>🐈 GAME MODE 🐈</strong><br>Chase other cats as a tagger. Force them join your sides. Take over the whole map. OR play as a coward runner and never get caught. Its up to you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142960/extras/1028e3c4feb604446c4a8